    • Constructor Detail

      • CardGroup5

        public CardGroup5()
        Constructor for a CardGroup5 object. The attribute SPEC_TYPE is randomly generated between the integers 1 and 5.

        The SPEC_TYPE attribute dictates what the value of dChangeRate will be and the OwnableSpace subclasses that instances of this class can be applied to.

    • Method Detail

      • isCardApplicable

        public boolean isCardApplicable(Player player)
        Checking method for an instance of this class and an instance of Player.

        The checking returns true if any of the following are satisfied.

        • SPEC_TYPE = 1: player owns at least one instance of Property.
        • SPEC_TYPE = 2: player owns at least one instance of Property.
        • SPEC_TYPE = 3: player owns at least one instance of Property.
        • SPEC_TYPE = 4: player owns at least one instance of Railroad or Utility.
        Parameters:
        player - Player object whose ownedSpaces will be checked for possible card application.
        Returns:
        Boolean variable that is true if the card is indeed applicable to an OwnableSpace that the player owns.

      • applyCardToSpace

        public double applyCardToSpace(OwnableSpace space)
        Method that applies the effects of an instance to an OwnableSpace.
        Parameters:
        space - OwnableSpace object whose dMultiplier attribute will be modified.
        Returns:
        Integer that is greater than 1 if payment needs to be made after the application of an instance.
